  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA48-kiḷavi">itu pirivuṇarttiya talaivaṟkut tōḻi colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is what the confidante said to HIM who informed [her] about the separation.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA48">
<l>            aṉṟai yaṉaiya vāki yiṉṟumeṅ</l>
<l>            kaṇṇuḷ pōlac cuḻalu mātō</l>
<l>            pullitaḻk kōṅkiṉ mellitaḻk kuṭaippū</l>
<l>            vaikuṟu mīṉi ṉiṉaiyat tōṉṟip</l>
<l>            puṟavaṇi koṇṭa pūnāṟu kaṭattiṭaik </l>
<l>            kiṭiṉeṉa viṭikkuṅ kōṟṟoṭi maṟavar</l>
<l>            vaṭinavi lampiṉ viṉaiya rañcā</l>
<l>            tamariṭai yuṟutara nīkkinī</l>
<l>            remariṭai yuṟutara voḷitta kāṭē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent3">Being such on that day, are they [still] spinning</l>
<l>today, as if inside our eyes?</l>
<l>– the wild places</l>
<l rend="indent">where you, not afraid of those whose occupation are the sharp sounding arrows,</l>
<l rend="indent2">the bold ones with bracelets clinking beautiful 'kiṭiṉ',</l>
<l rend="indent2">having repelled their people when they occurred in between,</l>
<l rend="indent">were concealed when our people occurred in between,</l>
<l rend="indent2">in the middle of the wilderness fragrant with flowers</l>
<l rend="indent2">which are taken as adornment of the woodland,</l>
<l rend="indent2">appearing, when one thinks [of them](?),<note place="foot">What is the function of <term xml:lang="ta">niṉaiya</term> here?</note> like stars at dawn,</l>
<l rend="indent2">the flowers with parasols of soft petals on the low-petalled(?) Kōṅku tree.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
          </body>
